item.title: CVE-2023-29187|2023-04-11T03:09:31.468Z -- sap -- sapsetup%20%28software%20installation%20program%29
item.description: A Windows user with basic user authorization can exploit a DLL hijacking attack in SapSetup (Software Installation Program) - version 9.0, resulting in a privilege escalation running code as administrator of the very same Windows PC. A successful attack depends on various preconditions beyond the attackers control.
